WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Veristake. Insurance claims, verified by economics.

00:08.000 --> 00:22.000
A denied ER claim becomes a structured appeal packet.

00:22.000 --> 00:35.000
Independent reviewers vote, resolve the dispute, and release payout.

00:35.000 --> 00:50.000
Pacific Mutual registers a policy and funds its carrier reserve.

00:50.000 --> 01:05.000
Live claims resolve from the reserve with a visible audit trail.

01:05.000 --> 01:20.000
Verifiers review three claims and catch the fraud pattern.

01:20.000 --> 01:30.000
Open the demo, review the dashboard, and book an integration call.
